data = JSON.parse("[{\"id\":367,\"lat\":\"51.511207\",\"lng\":\"-0.119225\",\"time\":\"2016-07-14T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Strand\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was in Stratford, walking down the streets. My mother sent me to collect something from her friend. I was unable to due to my phone as the battery life was running out \\u0026 switched off all itself. I went to the Lebera phone shop. I asked the retail assistant to charge my phone \\u0026 he did charged it. Then my phone was charged (not fully charged at time as my phone battery life was around 15 to 10%). I called my mother to say that I am not happy with her, sending me out without realising my phone was at low percentage of battery life. I argued with her on the phone and then my phone went goes off again as I recalled moaning. Then suddenly, out of nowhere, the man (white British, who wore brown or grey coat \\u0026 looked middle aged) stuck his noise in a business that does not concern him. He said to me that \\\"this is England, this is Britain, that is not how you talk in this country\\\" I said to the guy in a calm way \\\"that got nothing to do with you sir\\\" then he talked to me rudely \\u0026 harassed me by verbally abusing me, while saying \\\"it's not how you communicate \\u0026 behave in this country, etc\\\". I kept repeating to the person who was racist \\u0026 very rude \\u0026 interfere the business that does not concern. \\\"It has nothing got to do with you sir\\\". He said to me \\\"Don't call me sir\\\". I am black British. I was born in this country the UK \\u0026 I lived here in this country all my life. I never experienced racism before. My parents are from Africa (mum - South African \\u0026 dad - Nigerian).  This is the UK who used to had the biggest empire in the world \\u0026 now victimising the foreigners \\u0026 EU nationals because the whole country voted to leave the European Union.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Amatare\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:09:16.605Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:31:04.967Z\",\"support\":\"Yes. Someone (caucasian, another word for white) came up to me in a rescue \\u0026 told me \\\"Ignore the man, he is drunk\\\" as he was kind and polite to me. I said \\\"okay\\\" so I ignored the person who was being disrespectful \\u0026 verbally abused me. I walked away \\u0026 the person who was racist to me, walked away too. \"},{\"id\":366,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-06-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Unknown Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Lackareagh\",\"description\":\"Me and my family was shocked to witness an incident while we was visiting Ireland. We came over from China and we was having a great time when a man with grey hair did Hitler signs at my family through the window. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Co. Clare\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T19:05:26.819Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:50:12.191Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":364,\"lat\":\"51.428825\",\"lng\":\"-0.547876\",\"time\":\"2016-07-21T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Runnymede District\",\"description\":\"Recently moved to the area. Tracksuited youth of about 14 or 15 told me to \\\"go back to São Tomé and Príncipe\\\" before saying something along the lines of \\\"too many São Tomé and Príncipians are stealing our jobs\\\".\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"tw200rb \",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Surrey\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T18:35:49.891Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:32:12.400Z\",\"support\":\"No one helped, another old man in his garden also expressed his hatred of São Tomé and Príncipians\"},{\"id\":363,\"lat\":\"53.795984\",\"lng\":\"-1.759398\",\"time\":\"2016-07-06T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Thorncliffe Rd\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bradford District\",\"description\":\"I was racially abused by anti-semites outside my local synagogue\\r\\nthe I was verbally attacked by a gang of middle eastern youths who called me all sorts of names like 'butcher' or 'vampire' or 'monster'\\r\\nI quickly tried to hurry past them as they spat at me and insulted me viciously when a car suddenly came out of nowhere and some racist goys started throwing bacon, chicken nuggets and prawns at us from their car window while yelling racist slogans like 'fuck off we're full' and 'this is our england'\\r\\nthe youths scattered at the sight of the bacon and since shellfish and pork products arent kosher I ended up having to crawl under a nearby mitsubishi verada sedan as it rained streaks of bacon and rotten prawns all around us\\r\\nat this point the youths seemed to have forgotten about me and decided to attack the car carrying the racists who then sped off with one of them pointing their arse out the window and taking a shit onto the street\\r\\nwhile the youths chased the car i quickly scuttled out from under my hiding place over the non-kosher prawns and ran to the Bradford Reform Synagogue where I had to be calmed down by my Rabbi\\r\\nI am absolutely appalled by this behaviour, I emigrated to the UK from Israel 20 years ago to set up my jewelers in Bradford and I am ashamed that the jewish community still has to suffer these racist attacks from bigots\\r\\nI voted leave in the Bremain referendum and I hang an EU flag from my front window right next to my Israeli flag I'm just as British as the next person and I demand to be treated fairly\\r\\nI only hope when the labour party gets back into power that they can fix all these racists and stop their attacks\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Yorkshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Mr Zedekiah Schwarz\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T18:34:15.752Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:32:59.924Z\",\"support\":\"When I went to my Synagogue and told them about what happened my community members were all shocked and appalled at what I had just suffered and needless to say the jewish community in Bradford stands with the message of multiculturalism and diversity as it is the only way to defeat these racists\\r\\n\"},{\"id\":347,\"lat\":\"52.92253\",\"lng\":\"-1.474619\",\"time\":\"2016-05-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Peach street \",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Derby\",\"description\":\"I am a white woman with a mixed race child who I was walking home from the park in the late afternoon, as I turned on to a quiet side-street just a few minutes walk from my home I saw a quite intimidating looking white man. He was tall, lean, bearded and was staring directly into my eyes as he walked my way, obviously travelling in the opposite direction. I was frightened so I looked at the ground and tried to make a plenty of space for the man, I'm ashamed that I allowed myself to be intimidated by this man who I guess was at least 5 years my junior but I am a single mother living in a rather deprived area with nobody to turn to, what could I possibly do?\\r\\n\\r\\nAs he walked on past me, casting a large shadow over me and my daughter he told me in a calm and well spoken manner that my daughter is a 'mongrel'. \\r\\n\\r\\nWe were both upset, our wonderful day had been ruined.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Derby\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:26:06.503Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:41:12.674Z\",\"support\":\"There were two black men walking on the other side of the road when it happened, I'm sure they heard what he said to me and my daughter but they said nothing.\"},{\"id\":345,\"lat\":\"53.407622\",\"lng\":\"-2.977313\",\"time\":\"2016-06-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Lime Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Liverpool\",\"description\":\"It was late at night and I was locking the doors of my synagogue when I turned around and heard in the distance \\\"we know\\\" I thought to myself what do they know? Then a rock hit me and it read on the side \\\"Im glad the 6 gorrilion suffocated\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"L1 1JD\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Merseyside\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:18:58.833Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:57:02.400Z\",\"support\":\"I told my friends at the synagogue and they suggested keep reinforcing the message of diversity to counter their hate. \"},{\"id\":344,\"lat\":\"53.47404\",\"lng\":\"-2.24199\",\"time\":\"2016-06-09T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Manchester\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the street and I quickly noticed the air blow against the top of my head, I knew imidietly that my yarmulke had been stolen, I turned around and a tall man dressed as a green frog was laughing and shouting \\\" Oy vey you can't shut me down kike\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater Manchester\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T15:05:27.991Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:41:44.262Z\",\"support\":\"People who were coming out the pub joined in and started chanting \\\"Oy vey\\\" over and over again.\"},{\"id\":343,\"lat\":\"52.468164\",\"lng\":\"-1.854315\",\"time\":\"2015-06-18T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Coventry Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Birmingham\",\"description\":\"Several times have I walked through the small heath area with a couple of freind of mine in both broad daylight and night and been told to \\\"fuck off and go to your own area\\\". It's not so bad near the larger supermarket chains, but the further you get into the highstreet the more racial abuse I get from several different communities. I have been refused service by one or two of the local store chains and now avoid the area completely. The vast majority, though not agreeing with the attackers do not seem to care too much about it.\\r\\nThis is a mostly MiddleEastern area and not all the communities are bad, but some are absolutley terrible and cross group racial incidents are extremely frequent.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Midlands\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:56:15.612Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:42:15.231Z\",\"support\":\"I have had one or two speak up, but only a few times over several minor incidents. Luckily only one has involved a physical altercation, with a boxcutter knife of which ended up with me having to run for my life. This incident was reported to police but I never felt it worth telling to anyone else since the suspects were caught in the end for a fatal stabbing some time later.\"},{\"id\":342,\"lat\":\"51.505785\",\"lng\":\"-0.43098\",\"time\":\"2016-07-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Dawley Road\",\"house\":\"1-3\",\"town\":\"Uxbridge\",\"description\":\"I am an orthodox Jewish man. Walking down a street in west London I was approached by a gang of what I can only describe as \\\"skinheads\\\", who accosted me abruptly with the words \\\"Hey Chaim, want some shekels, greedy Jew?\\\", with which they started throwing 1 \\u0026 2pence coins at the ground around me. I don't know how they guessed my name. I politely asked them to stop and tried to quickly move away but they followed me chanting \\\"oy vey, it's a shoah, the goyim know\\\". A shoah is a holocaust! I told them my grandfather perished in the holocaust and they chanted, quite loudly \\\"six million more, lock the gas chamber door\\\" over and over again. I was almost moved to tears by this.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"UB8 3JU\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:43:01.806Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:42:34.176Z\",\"support\":\"No one seemed to care, heads down as if to pretend it wasn't happening.\"},{\"id\":340,\"lat\":\"51.596482\",\"lng\":\"-0.108943\",\"time\":\"2016-07-13T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Haringey\",\"description\":\"i was travelling on the 29 bus when a black man called me a \\\"turkroach\\\" and told me that there was a storm brewing and people would be removing kebabs like me very soon \\r\\n \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"mehmet ozturk\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:20:53.741Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:43:12.576Z\",\"support\":\"people ignored \"},{\"id\":337,\"lat\":\"51.461305\",\"lng\":\"-0.303771\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Richmond upon Thames\",\"description\":\"I was at Peter Oliver Library, renewing my books, when two middle aged men walked up to me and said that this Library had been around since 1488 and that it was apart of British history and that I was insulting them being there as a foreigner. I've never experienced anything like this until after the Brexit. I don't feel safe anymore.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Samaira\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T14:01:22.712Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:45:33.783Z\",\"support\":\"Yes, thankfully the librarian told them men to leave and offered to call the police for me.\"},{\"id\":325,\"lat\":\"54.978252\",\"lng\":\"-1.61778\",\"time\":\"2016-07-21T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Newcastle upon Tyne\",\"description\":\"i was in greggs getting a steak bake and someone called me a 'black bastard'\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Tyne and Wear\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:28:46.291Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:39:12.967Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":323,\"lat\":\"54.136878\",\"lng\":\"-1.523581\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Market Place West\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Ripon\",\"description\":\"I was called turkroach and kebab lover in Greggs, they claimed it was just banter but even the staff were laughing. There's clearly institutional racism there, perhaps due to Harrogate not being very diverse. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"HG4 1BW\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"North Yorkshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Hüseyin Öztürk\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:25:53.224Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:38:26.233Z\",\"support\":\"No one, literally disgusted, they were all laughing or smirking. \"},{\"id\":321,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-16T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was on holiday from Finland and a group of English people told me to \\\"fuck off back to Mongolia\\\".\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:09:32.506Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:13:26.303Z\",\"support\":\"No.\"},{\"id\":314,\"lat\":\"51.885377\",\"lng\":\"-2.183015\",\"time\":\"2016-06-26T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Craven Drive\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Gloucester\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the street and heard what sounded like a Polish man calling a man of Pakistani origin to 'go home and kiss Muhammad'.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"GL3 2DZ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Gloucestershire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"S. Russ\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T12:59:37.150Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:37:03.167Z\",\"support\":\"No-one spoke up. \"},{\"id\":308,\"lat\":\"52.458257\",\"lng\":\"-1.929457\",\"time\":\"2016-07-19T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Farquhar Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Birmingham\",\"description\":\"Man leaned out of his car window as he drove past and shouted \\\"we voted to leave, gas the kikes, race war now\\\" to some Jewish students\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"B15 2QP\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Midlands\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Adam Cohen\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T12:38:18.334Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:10:56.518Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":299,\"lat\":\"51.724513\",\"lng\":\"-1.995882\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Cotswold District\",\"description\":\"I saw a teenaged blonde girl point and laugh at a Turban wearing man who was playing Jenga, I think he was Sikh or something. She imitated a flying plane and ran into his Jenga  towers, causing them to fall everywhere.  \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Gloucestershire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-21T00:51:31.951Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T23:36:40.188Z\",\"support\":\"A group of asian tourists who seemed to be with the girl joined in and started laughing at the poor man.\"},{\"id\":289,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-06-23T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Sussex Gardens\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the Sussex gardens with my wife and her new boyfriend when an elderly man approached my wife's boyfriend and started yelling ethnic slurs at him and sexist slurs at my wife( Calling him a paki who should go back to his sand castle, and calling her an ugly bint among other things). I was so offended by this that I was moved to tears. the man then threatened my wifes boyfriend with a pistol(I think it was airsoft)before I told him that England is a gun free zone, Thankfully he realized his wrongdoing at this point and left.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-20T23:44:17.627Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:12:32.526Z\",\"support\":\"My Wife's boyfriend was strong enough in the moment to provide support by putting his hand on my shoulder and telling me it's alright. Most of the other people were too offended or scared to intervene.\"},{\"id\":288,\"lat\":\"51.435473\",\"lng\":\"0.020279\",\"time\":\"2016-07-20T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Lewisham\",\"description\":\"I was speaking in German with my family as we wandered past the station, an onlooking bystander nudged his friend mumbling something about Bomber Harris.\\r\\n\\r\\nI heard what he said and chose to ignore it, but then his friends cut into our conversation by yelling \\\"Hey Krauts! Still sore about Dresden?\\\" sending his friend into a laughing fit beside him.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-20T23:35:55.180Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:06:11.685Z\",\"support\":\"Rather than offering support a shopkeeper who overheard the whole thing added as we walked past \\\"you sowed the wind, you reaped the whirlwind\\\", not taking notice that my wife was clearly upset by this point.\"},{\"id\":285,\"lat\":\"53.146403\",\"lng\":\"0.337881\",\"time\":\"2016-07-14T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"East Lindsey District\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the high street with my 3 year old daughter. I am a woman of colour from Finland. My little girl is too of colour. A man of about 60 on the other side of the street shouted \\\"go back to Mongolia, you f*cking chink\\\". My daughter and I broke down crying in the street. Many dozens walked by in the 10 minutes we sat there, the old man mocking us from a far. \\\"Fucking zipper-head gooks\\\".\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Lincolnshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-20T22:29:12.057Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T13:03:39.788Z\",\"support\":\"No one offered support; not surprising for the area (we're hoping to move to a more diverse town, like King's Lynn, after this incident).\"},{\"id\":282,\"lat\":\"57.586422\",\"lng\":\"-3.868475\",\"time\":\"2016-07-06T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Seabank Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Nairn\",\"description\":\"Was told to go back to Uzbekistan by a group of children.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Highland\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-20T22:10:48.775Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-21T12:59:30.206Z\",\"support\":\"no\"},{\"id\":281,\"lat\":\"52.912524\",\"lng\":\"-0.643582\",\"time\":\"2016-07-18T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"South Kesteven District\",\"description\":\"Work colleague shouted to me \\\"you foreign cunt\\\" in front of everyone in the office\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Lincolnshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Kathy\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-18T20:03:49.217Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-19T13:59:06.340Z\",\"support\":\"No one took any notice\"},{\"id\":280,\"lat\":\"55.975117\",\"lng\":\"-3.166243\",\"time\":\"2016-07-09T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Edinburgh\",\"description\":\"Neo- Nazi stickers(National Action) found in Leith Edinburgh Scotland.\\r\\nscrapped them off.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Edinburgh\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-17T08:56:53.207Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-18T08:57:27.294Z\",\"support\":\"No.\"},{\"id\":279,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-11T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"37 Shelfield Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Nelson\",\"description\":\"Someone said she will \\\"set our house on fire\\\" call me fucking Lithuanian cunt and silly cow, her 12 years old daughter said to my 8 year old girl \\\"Lithuanian bitch\\\".\\r\\n\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"BB9 8BY\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Lancashire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Brigita\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-14T10:34:48.666Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-14T13:50:52.728Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":278,\"lat\":\"50.726519\",\"lng\":\"-1.864899\",\"time\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bournemouth\",\"description\":\"Went to Asda day after referendum. Was told by 2 teenage boys, approx age 13-14  \\\" Oy, mate, this is England, it's OUR England now\\\"...adult male with them just watched and laughed.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"BH8 8DL\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Bournemouth\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Pedro Rozzi\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-13T16:36:27.609Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-13T18:55:36.539Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":277,\"lat\":\"51.857981\",\"lng\":\"-2.232618\",\"time\":\"2016-07-13T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Barton Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Gloucester\",\"description\":\"I was just on the Stagecoach number 1 bus from Gloucester City Centre to Barton Street. I suppose I got on the bus just before 16:00. Some school children got on at the same time as me and my three year old. I knew the bus driver, his surname is Turner. After a short while on the bus a man at the front of the bus good up and went over to a school child who was sat next to my little one in the disabled seats and told him to speak English. Stating he is in England so he must speak English. The child, obviously felt uncomfortable about this and tried to ignore him by speaking to his friend. Then he repeated himself to them and the child was talking to his friends saying things like \\\"who does this guy thing he is?\\\" and his friends were responding with comments on the rudeness. Then the elderly couple sat behind my child and this school child tapped the kid on the shoulder and told him to stop being so rude because the man had made this comment 'in good faith'. The child commented that he didn't want to be in England I this is how he is being treated the elderly of this couple said to him that he should leave the country. Then the man at the front said \\\"years ago Hitler tried to kill everyone like you and I can see why\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"GL1 4JJ\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Gloucestershire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Graeme Thorne \",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-13T15:19:23.457Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-13T16:02:03.397Z\",\"support\":\"Nobody said anything against the racism except for the school children who were supporting their peer. I wish I had spoken up but the man at the front was incredibly threatening. He looked a bit like the comedian Rich Hall, but skinnier and dirtier. \"},{\"id\":276,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Margate\",\"description\":\"A white man shouted at a young mixed race boy (probably 18) that he was a 'black bastard' during an exchange between them.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-13T1