code\":\"BN43 5HH\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"West Sussex\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-12T14:20:56.470Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-12T14:35:47.435Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":272,\"lat\":\"53.390044\",\"lng\":\"-2.59695\",\"time\":\"2016-06-27T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Warrington\",\"description\":\"I was with my parents in an M\\u0026S car park. We've got a Slovenian license plate and people were staring at us (we could see in the rear view mirror). Then someone shouted at us to say we shouldn't be there and should go home. And when we came back to our car someone had thrown litter all over it. My parents told me they'd been shouted at a few times in their car since Brexit. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Warrington\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-11T22:17:29.784Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-11T23:39:55.926Z\",\"support\":\"No one helped. \"},{\"id\":271,\"lat\":\"51.496998\",\"lng\":\"-0.025863\",\"time\":\"2016-07-11T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"At 3.30pm in Tower Hamlets (a predominantly Muslim and Bangladeshi area): the bus is full of children and parents going home when it starts to rain hard against the windows. A parent closes the window... a few seconds later the bus stops and the bus driver comes upstairs. He claims that whoever is making that noise needs to get off or he will not continue to drive the bus. Someone tells him it was someone just shutting a window - he then responds by saying \\\"oh, it better not be bombs or whatever going off up here\\\". \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-11T20:00:59.923Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-11T22:01:18.055Z\",\"support\":\"The bus just went incredibly silent, I think we were all a bit confused, but I was incredibly anger afterwards having thought about where that came from.\"},{\"id\":270,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-10T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Deansgate\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Manchester\",\"description\":\"I was walking down the street. An Asian guy was in front of me minding his own business when a white Middle Aged man walked into him and forced him against the wall saying move paki, move paki. Leave. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-11T13:17:16.577Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-11T14:26:32.087Z\",\"support\":\"I spoke up and told the guy to go or I'd call the police. He left and I asked the Asian man if he was ok. He said yes, he was used to it and walked off. \"},{\"id\":269,\"lat\":\"52.947769\",\"lng\":\"-1.177542\",\"time\":\"2016-07-03T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Hillside\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Nottingham\",\"description\":\"Was waiting for the bus last sunday morning when the british couple beside me started speaking rather loudly about how britain is for british and that they cant even go one day without seeing an immigrant around these days. As if me waiting for the bus with them totally ruined the start of their day. There was no one else there but me so I chose to just keep quiet and ignore it.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Nottinghamshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-10T21:26:49.059Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-10T23:09:24.600Z\",\"support\":\"No one else around\"},{\"id\":268,\"lat\":\"51.375801\",\"lng\":\"-2.359904\",\"time\":\"2016-07-10T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bath\",\"description\":\"Man screamed 'terrorist' from his car at passing pedestrian. Leaned out window screaming 'come at me, terrorist' repeatedly whilst banging car door.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Bath and North East Somerset\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-10T16:35:53.278Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-10T17:21:12.157Z\",\"support\":\"no one\"},{\"id\":267,\"lat\":\"51.171924\",\"lng\":\"-0.164606\",\"time\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Gatwick\",\"description\":\"On Tuesday 5th July I was on the 9am Gatwick to Lanzarote with my two children.  We were in row 2.  Halfway in to the flight, I heard the passenger directly behind me remark to his friend that he'd better start practising the limbo.  When his friend asked why, the man replied, \\\"because it's like being in the Caribbean with those darkies on here\\\".   I'm white, my children are mixed race.  Their father was black, and sadly died of cancer 5 years ago.  Tuesday 5th July would've been his birthday, which was why I chose that date to fly on - to give us a happy memory of the day.\\r\\n\\r\\nThankfully my little girls, who are just 6 and 8 years old did not hear the comments, and so were none the wiser.  I chose not to challenge the man for several reasons - he was big,  built of muscle and as a lone woman with 2 young children, I did not feel comfortable to do so.  And I didn't want my children to experience the potential fallout if I did challenge him. It was extremely upsetting though, and in my 20 odd years of travelling with non-white people (my husband for 15 years and subsequently my children), I have never experienced anything like this.\\r\\n\\r\\nFor the record, when I stood up and looked back in the plane, I could only see white faces.  However, if the plane was 99% black people, that comment would still have been completely unacceptable.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"RH6 0FH\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Surrey\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-09T18:09:54.671Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-09T19:40:13.704Z\",\"support\":\"No, no one did.\"},{\"id\":266,\"lat\":\"51.903761\",\"lng\":\"-0.196612\",\"time\":\"2016-07-06T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Stevenage\",\"description\":\"A black, heavily accented man working the till in a large supermarket started a conversation with me about how it was now cheaper for tourists to come visit Britain and more expensive for us to travel abroad. A man in the queue behind me interrupted to say \\\"Brexit was the best thing we ever done in the last 5 years.\\\" I think he meant to bully an obvious immigrant who was at work and alone and would hardly have been in a position to argue. I said I couldn't disagree more and said I was an immigrant (I'm American, but not obviously foreign-born). The Brexiteer puffed up his chest and went red in the face and said we should both just go home. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Hertfordshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-09T09:11:22.546Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-09T11:00:13.102Z\",\"support\":\"I did, but couldn't do much. The man working the till was desperate to smoothe things over because he was at work, and when he shot me anguished looks, I stopped arguing.\"},{\"id\":265,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Green Dragon Lane\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Brentford\",\"description\":\"Sitting in my car minding my own business waiting to carry out some training for guys working on a site close to Kew Bridge when a young lad approached my car and told me to 'f***off back to my own country, we showed you last week we dont want you here no more'\\r\\n\\r\\nI am an olive skinned white british person whose family have lived in the UK for over 300 years having emigrated here over 300 years ago.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Rick Barber\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T15:20:35.362Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:35:07.673Z\",\"support\":\"A couple of people passed at the time of the abuse but did nothing and I cannot apportion blame as you never know what might happen.\"},{\"id\":264,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Clayfields\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Basildon\",\"description\":\"In Basildon and approached by twenty something man who informed me I needed to return to my country. Then told me I obviously didnt understand a word he was saying 'you foreign f***wit'. Was then informed I should 'f***off' before Im stabbed or chucked out the country.\\r\\n\\r\\nJust to show how stupid this is and how ignorant people are, I am an olive skinned white britain whose family have lived in the UK for over 300 years having emigrated from northern france. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Rick Barber\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T15:11:18.370Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:34:27.528Z\",\"support\":\"No-one around it was 6am\"},{\"id\":262,\"lat\":\"51.58225\",\"lng\":\"-0.39658\",\"time\":\"2016-07-08T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Hillingdon\",\"description\":\"This morning before work, I was indicating to park, a white female sped up in her car going the opposite direction of the car park to try and take the parking space. She was annoyed that I didn't give the space to her (why should I, I was there before her) so waited till I got out the car to say to me, \\\"you people (me being a British Indian) should go back to where you are from! It is people like you who bring this country down!\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T14:35:40.913Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:33:48.531Z\",\"support\":\"A white woman came to ask the woman in the car if everything was okay. She remained relatively silent but seemed to support the woman in the car.\"},{\"id\":261,\"lat\":\"53.293182\",\"lng\":\"-3.72764\",\"time\":\"2016-03-01T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"93 Abergele Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Colwyn Bay\",\"description\":\"A woman at a bike shop told me: 'You sound foreign.' I said: 'Yepp.' Then she asked: 'What are you?' Perhaps it's not racist, but I was confused why would she say 'what' instead of 'who', or 'where are you from', or why would she ask at all.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"LL29 7SA\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Conwy\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T14:18:35.400Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:33:28.631Z\",\"support\":\"I was alone. Nobody spoke up.\"},{\"id\":260,\"lat\":\"51.342817\",\"lng\":\"-0.064421\",\"time\":\"2016-06-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London Borough of Croydon\",\"description\":\"My Polish neighbour was in our local park with her 2 1/2 year old daughter. They were approached by an older man in his 60's who started shouting abuse at them. \\r\\nHe shouted 'we voted to leave so why the f don't you go home. None of us want you here' \\r\\nThis continued for some time as she gathered her child and left the park. The only other person present was the man's grandson. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-08T11:47:24.401Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-08T21:33:17.197Z\",\"support\":\"No-one else present \"},{\"id\":259,\"lat\":\"52.531697\",\"lng\":\"0.830378\",\"time\":\"2016-07-07T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Thetford\",\"description\":\"I was called a 'stupid ape' (I'm black) by a woman in a pink Land Rover when I stopped to ask directions back to the main road.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"IP24 1PT\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Norfolk\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T19:16:25.324Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-07T21:01:16.220Z\",\"support\":\"I was alone.\"},{\"id\":258,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-06-22T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Cleveland Way\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Bethnal Green\",\"description\":\"I am reporting 2 incidents, that took place in the space of 24 hours.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe day before the EU referendum, my mixed-race friend of Chinese \\u0026 Candian heritage, Geni Lou, was scolded on the street with the \\\"Fucking Chink!\\\" in Bethnal Green, while walking home. The next day, my other friend Kieran Warner, of English \\u0026 Jamaican heritage, was harassed by what may seem to be the same woman, when he was at the polling station. The only intelligible part of her rant he understood was her saying \\\"I want things back to the way they used to be.\\\" When Kieran asked \\\"What about human rights \\u0026 woman's rights?\\\", she shouted back \\\"We never had no rights!\\\".\\r\\n\\r\\nThere are potentially more I could report, but when you're on the go \\u0026 in a rush, it's to stop \\u0026 be witness.\\r\\n\\r\\nI was also subject to racial abuse when I was taking a bus back to my temporary abode in Perth, Australia, last December 2015. If you have any information on where I can report this incident, that would be really appreciated. This happens to often \\u0026 I to do something pro-active about it, please.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"e1 4tz\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"East London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Ng, Chin-Yu.\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-07T14:45:32.416Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-0