il\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:41:50.975Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T16:13:24.933Z\",\"support\":\"No one stood up for her in the moment, but the venue staff immediately made sure the abuser was no longer on the premises and made sure other clubs in the area were aware of the incident. \"},{\"id\":219,\"lat\":\"51.598956\",\"lng\":\"-0.097306\",\"time\":\"2016-07-02T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Lordship Lane\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"Walking along Lordship Lane in Tottenham, London a man shouted across the street staring at my husband:\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\"I'm going to open up and cut fucking pakis\\\". \\r\\n\\r\\nI shouted at him to shut up and he did.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N22 5BY\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:40:33.380Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T16:13:11.721Z\",\"support\":\"Me - I shouted at the man\"},{\"id\":218,\"lat\":\"51.334821\",\"lng\":\"-0.478814\",\"time\":\"2016-06-30T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Rectory Lane\",\"house\":\"46\",\"town\":\"West Byfleet\",\"description\":\"I am an American-born British citizen. My daughter also has dual-citizenship. My husband is Scottish. We have an EU flag in our front window. \\r\\n\\r\\nLast Thursday I returned home from taking my one year old daughter to her Aquatots swim class. \\r\\n\\r\\nA man at the bus stop in front of our house in West Byfleet, Surrey, must have heard me speaking with a neighbour about his dog (whom my daughter loves). As I walked to the door, carrying my daughter, the man at the bus stop shouted \\\"Time to take that flag down Love\\\" in a very sarcastic way. I mildly responded \\\"thanks, but I might leave it up.\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nAs I opened my front door, the man shouted \\\"What the fuck do you know, you're not even British!\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nI went inside and locked the door, and didn't engage with the man. I was worried at first because I had my 14 month old, and the man felt very hostile.\\r\\n\\r\\nI'm no longer scared, just disappointed and angry. I have lived in this country for 27 years. I am the General Counsel (Head of Legal) for the Royal Pharmaceutical Society of Great Britain. I pay taxes, and I have devoted a lot of time to local charities.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"KT14 7LU\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Surrey\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"Kimberly Shields\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:38:44.207Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T16:13:00.364Z\",\"support\":\"No one else was around. The neighbour with the dog had just left.\"},{\"id\":217,\"lat\":\"51.575656\",\"lng\":\"-0.225782\",\"time\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"I was doing some food shopping and an Eastern European man accidentally bumped an older lady's trolley as he went past. She turned to him and aggressively said \\\"People like you are the reason I voted Brexit - get all you bloody foreigners out of here.\\\"\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"NW4 3FP\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:38:27.193Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T16:12:22.994Z\",\"support\":\"The man told her to calm down and to leave him alone and left the situation. I was stunned for a minute and then I had to go up to her and tell her that she is an ignorant old woman and she should be mortified.\\r\\n\\r\\nLeft the shop after that.\"},{\"id\":216,\"lat\":\"51.147435\",\"lng\":\"0.328828\",\"time\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"High Street\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Tunbridge Wells\",\"description\":\"I received a letter through a letter box this morning with really badly written text on it saying: \\\"Fuck off to Poland\\\". The text looked like it was purposely written with really bad writing to mislead. The letter was together with couple of other small parcels. Could it be the post man? NO IDEA...\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Kent\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:06:25.379Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:37:29.485Z\",\"support\":\"I reported it to the Kent Police and I will questioned tomorrow.\"},{\"id\":215,\"lat\":\"50.461921\",\"lng\":\"-3.525315\",\"time\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Torquay\",\"description\":\"\\\"EU Rats. Go Home Now\\\". Graffiti on side of Health Centre in Torquay.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Torbay\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:05:46.558Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T15:37:00.353Z\",\"support\":\"Reported to police\"},{\"id\":214,\"lat\":\"50.375457\",\"lng\":\"-4.142656\",\"time\":\"2016-06-10T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Plymouth\",\"description\":\"I was stood outside a shop a while back, waiting for my dad to get something and I heard someone foreign walk past two women and they were talking in another language, one of the two women then said 'Why the fuck do we have so many fucking foreigners? Learn to speak English for fucks sake!'\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Plymouth\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T13:20:15.320Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T13:53:15.621Z\",\"support\":\"No one said anything.\"},{\"id\":213,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-07-08T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Burton upon trent\",\"description\":\"'This is England' someone muttered in the charity shop while I was chatting in French to my mum. To be honest I completely dismissed it as a stupid person's comment and didn't even register it until I got out.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T13:14:42.127Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T13:53:04.255Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":212,\"lat\":\"51.590428\",\"lng\":\"-0.102759\",\"time\":\"2016-05-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Westbury Avenue\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"My wife and I are in a mixed-race relationship (white and Anglo-Caribbean), early 30s. On May 5th 2016 we were walking into Turnpike Lane station at midday when we heard a man shouting. We turned to see a well dressed white man in his mid-40s, obviously inebriated, shouting unintelligibly at a black woman at the bus stop. He noticed us and said \\\"its bad enough all these niggers here, but when you see a white man betraying his race, like this bossman and his nigger bitch . . .\\\" whereupon he stopped talking as I had one hand around his throat. I was dragged away by my wife before I could strike the man, but as we left he continued his tirade against us, following to the entrance of the station but not following us inside.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"N15 3NX\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater London\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:04:26.753Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:51:05.642Z\",\"support\":\"No. There was a crowd of at least 30 people within ear shot, evenly spilt white and black, but no one said anything or intervened, although all looked shocked.\"},{\"id\":211,\"lat\":\"54.77525\",\"lng\":\"-1.584852\",\"time\":\"2016-06-25T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"City centre\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Durham\",\"description\":\"My daughters friend, who is bilingual as her mother is German, had to stop speaking in German with her mother in Durham City as people were passing remarks about bloody foreigners.  Durham is a multi cultural University City with funding from University of Japan for its science facilities.  Disgraceful that people should behave in this way.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"County Durham\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T10:33:33.440Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:50:34.169Z\",\"support\":\"People said and did nothing\"},{\"id\":210,\"lat\":\"53.54093\",\"lng\":\"-2.111366\",\"time\":\"2016-07-05T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Oldham District\",\"description\":\"I was out shopping with my wife and a white middle aged man approached me an wife and said \\\"we don't want you paki muslim here fuck off to your own country\\\". I was shocked and stunned by the comments. I didn't say anything in response because I didn't know what else he might do. This was deeply upsetting and has meant that we are now more cautious about what time we go shopping. What upsetted me the most was the fact that i was born here.\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Greater Manchester\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T10:21:25.227Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:50:17.292Z\",\"support\":\"No one said anything. People were just looking and staring. Not a single person challenged his behaviour. \"},{\"id\":209,\"lat\":\"53.193392\",\"lng\":\"-2.893075\",\"time\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Chester\",\"description\":\"This happened the day after the vote. I was at work and a coworker approached me with the cheerful greeting of: Oh, you're still haven't left the country!\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"Cheshire West and Chester\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T10:13:40.418Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:50:00.707Z\",\"support\":\"\"},{\"id\":208,\"lat\":null,\"lng\":null,\"time\":\"2016-06-29T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\" 1A Festing Rd\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Portsmouth\",\"description\":\"Walked into a pub in Portsmouth, we were having a good time and after half hour we went outside to have a cigarette, when I finished smoking as I was waking my way back into the pub, a man shout at \\\"This pub is only for locals mate, fuck off back to you own country\\\" I laughed and told him I only live around the corner and I am a local. \",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"PO4 0NG\",\"country\":\"\",\"region\":\"Hampshire\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T10:00:26.040Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:49:28.230Z\",\"support\":\"No one said anything. No support.\"},{\"id\":207,\"lat\":\"50.854259\",\"lng\":\"0.573453\",\"time\":\"2016-07-04T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"Hastings District\",\"description\":\"foreign exchange students was minding their own business walking through town, 2 middle aged white men started to shout 'f**k off back home' to them. The students looked about 15 years old, and scared. \\r\\n\\r\\n\",\"summary\":null,\"approved\":true,\"postcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"United Kingdom\",\"region\":\"East Sussex\",\"email\":null,\"name\":\"\",\"created_at\":\"2016-07-05T09:54:39.498Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2016-07-05T11:49:46.839Z\",\"support\":\"As soon as one person had ago at the men, others followed. \"},{\"id\":206,\"lat\":\"51.531387\",\"lng\":\"-0.114198\",\"time\":\"2016-06-24T00:00:00.000Z\",\"address\":null,\"street\":\"Pentonville Road\",\"house\":\"\",\"town\":\"London\",\"description\":\"Walking down the street on pentonville Road, London.  I man walking next to me kept shouting 'foreinger' at me.  We walked in different directions but when i paths crossed again, he shouted 'forei